The Corporation shall include, as part of its annual report to the Governor and the General Assembly under § 10-415 of this subtitle, a detailed description of:
the number of technology transfer transactions or projects for which the Initiative provided funding;
the amount and source of funds the Initiative identified to assist in the development of technologies;
the qualifying universities or entities for which funding was awarded;
the commercial value of technology that was transferred to the commercial industry; and
any recommendations for improving the overall effectiveness of technology transfer through the Initiative.
